IMP_DATA_MAP.sql_text: select sql_text from imp_data_map where length(sql_text) > 0

RULE.sql_text: select sql_text from rule where is_enabled = 1

RULE_CLASS_PARAM_VALUE.v.value_clob: select v.value_clob from rule_class_param_value v join rule r on (r.rule_id = v.rule_id) where r.is_enabled = 1

WF_STEP.s.plsql_block: select s.plsql_block from wf_step s join wf_workflow w on (w.wf_workflow_id = s.wf_workflow_id) where w.wf_state_id not in (4,5)

CONFIG_FIELD.sql_query: select sql_query from config_field where config_field_name <> 'XITOR_CLASS_ID'

GRID_PAGE_FIELD.param1: select param1 from grid_page_field where cell_renderer_id = 78

IMP_ENTITY_REQ_FIELD.sql_text: select sql_text from imp_entity_req_field where length(sql_text) > 0

TM_SETUP.search_sql: select search_sql from tm_setup where length(search_sql) > 0

IMP_ENTITY.sql_text: select sql_text from imp_entity where dbms_lob.getlength(sql_text) > 0
